{"tid":1350582,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"LingU仔全部同我入嚟!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:03:27.000Z","uid":121048,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"07114c1ec7f3815c2c9a7a2595ad445a217faa2c","tid":1350582,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:13:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱開咗係吹水台，依架開多次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知依架嶺事館嗰邊搞緊聯署，準備聲討何君堯條仆街校董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聯署Link: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScY3Ke7BQ9JBBfZho89j4FXFiJICyZc8t6VckQDSZFHD5ID0g/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScY3Ke7BQ9JBBfZho89j4FXFiJICyZc8t6VckQDSZFHD5ID0g%2Fviewform&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=e13c0879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScY3Ke7BQ9JBBfZho89j4FXFiJICyZc8t6VckQDSZFHD5ID0g/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n但係要預咗學校方面或者何妖係唔會有咩實際行動，最多出篇聲名噏下廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地要諗定點樣將行動升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有少少建議:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一: 全體學生罷交學費<br />\n二: 圍堵校務處/校長宿舍<br />\n三: 九月開學全校罷課<br />\n四: NSO開學禮嘅時候，將dem cheer環節改為高呼口號<br />\n五: 搞遊行&amp;連儂牆呢啲基本野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLingU仔就算係八大之尾，但都要有骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嶺大之恥，恥與為伍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求罷免何君堯嶺大校董一職</span></span>"},{"pid"